dc:description: Pale yellowish green glass. Part of body, rim and most of neck missing. Neck fragment included. Material fair. Some bubbles. Surface scratched. Brown milky weathering. Small flask. Spherical body. Concave base. Four horizontal shallow grooves below middle of body. A group of horizontal scratches above the base and a horizontal incision below the shoulder.
